text: Soni Jwalakwe ni Ajula jwantesile ŵanganyammwe kuŵa ŵawinjila pachilambo (panyuma pakwajonanga ŵakala), ni ŵanyakwile pa uchimbichimbi ŵane mwajenumanja pachanya pa ŵane kuti an'dije mayeso pa ichindu yampele, chisimu Ambuje ŵenu ni ŵachitema pakupeleka ipotesi, nambo soni Ŵalakweo ni Ŵakululuka kusyene, Ŵachanasa channope
